\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 REGAL = Galinpepimut-S (GPS) in AML CR2
\f1\b0 \
So the poster's biological framing\'a0
\f3\i is
\f1\i0 \'a0correct for the disease \'97 AML CR2 not eligible for transplant genuinely is relentlessly aggressive with a short natural history tail. That part holds up.\
GPS is a WT1-targeting peptide cancer vaccine designed to generate cytotoxic T-cell responses against WT1-expressing leukemic blasts. The mechanism is immunological \'97 you're trying to train the immune system to maintain remission surveillance.\
\

\f2\b Does a cure fraction make more sense here?
\f1\b0 \
Arguably\'a0
\f2\b more than most AML contexts
\f1\b0 , because:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Vaccine-based immunotherapy is one of the few mechanisms where durable immune memory could theoretically produce a genuine cure fraction \'97 you're not just killing blasts, you're potentially establishing persistent immunosurveillance\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 AML CR2 patients who\'a0
\f3\i do
\f1\i0 \'a0achieve long remissions on immunotherapy are genuinely outliers relative to historical controls, not just the natural tail of the disease\
\ls4\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The WT1 antigen is highly expressed and relatively tumor-specific, which supports durable T-cell targeting\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 But the modeling critique still stands
\f1\b0 \
Even if the biology is more supportive, the\'a0
\f2\b statistical inference problem is the same
\f1\b0 :\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Two event count anchors fitted to 6 model families is still underdetermined\
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The control arm KM shape is still being ignored\
\ls5\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 "99.99%" is still indefensible\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 The biology makes the cure-fraction hypothesis more\'a0
\f3\i plausible
\f1\i0 \'a0\'97 it doesn't validate the specific model or the probability claim.\
What's your current take on GPS's actual trial data?\
