\f1 \cf2 \strokec2 Yes, absolutely \'97 and this is actually one of the most interesting angles for GPS specifically because\'a0
\f2\b HLA type is central to how peptide vaccines work
\f1\b0 .\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b \cf2 Why HLA matters enormously for GPS
\f1\b0 \
GPS is a peptide vaccine targeting WT1. Peptide vaccines require the peptide to be\'a0
\f2\b presented on MHC class I molecules
\f1\b0 \'a0to activate cytotoxic T-cells. The presentation efficiency is highly HLA-allele dependent. So patients with certain HLA types will mount much stronger responses than others.\
\

\f2\b What to search on PubMed
\f1\b0 \
Try these search strings:\
