\f2\b \cf2 The intuition
\f1\b0 \
At month 36, the 26.2% cure fraction is already "banked" as a floor \'97 those patients are essentially at zero hazard. The remaining 73.8% who aren't cured contribute only their Weibull survival probability, which by month 36 has decayed substantially.\
As t 
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  \uc0\u8734 , S_susceptible(t) 
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f1  0, so the whole curve plateaus at exactly\'a0
\f2\b \uc0\u960  = 26.2%
\f1\b0 . That plateau is the visual cure fraction signature you saw in the Phase 2 KM curves.\

\f2\b BAT has no cure fraction
\f1\b0 , so it's just a pure Weibull with no floor \'97 which is why it hits near 0% by month 48.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

