\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs21 \cf15 \cb16 \strokec15 0.5 = exp(-(median/\uc0\u955 )^k)\
ln(0.5) = -(median/\uc0\u955 )^k\
\uc0\u955  = median / (ln(2)^(1/k))\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

