\fs21 \cf17 \cb16 \strokec17 def\cf15 \strokec15  \cf21 \strokec21 weibull_hazard\cf18 \strokec18 (\cf15 \strokec15 t\cf18 \strokec18 ,\cf15 \strokec15  median_os\cf18 \strokec18 ,\cf15 \strokec15  shape\cf18 \strokec18 ):\cf15 \strokec15 \
