\f1\b0 \
If you can get the REGAL interim KM curves from a conference presentation or SEC filing and digitize them with WebPlotDigitizer, you could\'a0
\f2\b fit both parameters simultaneously
\f1\b0 \'a0using maximum likelihood estimation:\
\
