\f2\b \cf2 Start with what the vaccine actually does
\f1\b0 \
GPS generates immune responses through two parallel pathways that can operate somewhat independently:\

\f2\b Pathway 1 \'97 Direct CD8+ route (HLA-A*02:01\'a0restricted)
