\f2\b \cf2 The honest uncertainty
\f1\b0 \
The chain is well grounded at the top \'97 HLA frequencies are solid population data. It gets progressively less certain as you go down:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls54\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 CD8+ response rate (86%) \'97 from Phase 2, but n=7\
\ls54\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 CD4+ response rate (44-57%) \'97 from Phase 2 and MM data, small n\
\ls54\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
