\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 So the 30-35% aggregate \uc0\u960  is a reasonable central estimate but the confidence interval around it is wide. The value of the model isn't the point estimate \'97 it's the sensitivity analysis showing you how much the conclusion changes as those uncertain parameters move around.\
