\f2\b \cf2 The important caveat
\f1\b0 \
Those CD4+ responders in Phase 2 weren't exclusively HLA-A
\f3\i 02:01- patients \'97 some were probably HLA-A
\f1\i0 02:01+ patients who mounted both CD4+ and CD8+ responses simultaneously. So the "none relapsed" observation may be driven partly by the combined CD4+/CD8+ response in HLA-A
\f3\i 02:01+ patients rather than CD4+ alone. That would mean P(cure | CD4 response, HLA-A
\f1\i0 02:01-) is somewhat lower than P(cure | CD4 response overall).\
